   Ionic Framework               : @ionic/angular 5.3.3
   @angular-devkit/build-angular : 0.1001.2
   @angular-devkit/schematics    : 10.1.2
   @angular/cli                  : 10.1.2
   @ionic/angular-toolkit        : 2.3.3

Capacitor:

   Capacitor CLI   : 2.4.1
